{{Infobox Berry |name = Tamato |image = [[File:Tamato.png]] |caption = This Berry is large and spicy. When eaten during the cold season, it warms the body from inside. |growtime = 2h 24m 0s |harvest = 25 berries |replant = 20% |points = 625 |flavor = {{!}} 20 {{!}} 10 {{!}} 0 {{!}} 0 {{!}} 0 }} '''Tamato''' is a type of [[Berries|Berry]] that can be planted in [[Farm]]. It can be obtained by surrounding a [[Razz]] with at least 1 [[Pomeg]]. The [[Razz]] will then have a chance to mutate into this berry.
